channel.title: Buttons stopped working
channel.description:
I don't know why. I haven't touched my files in a long time and I never changed anything but suddenly now many buttons don't work anymore.
The only thing that's happened is when I imported the project to Eclipse because I had to redownload it, it was at first giving me a bunch of errors and I had to clean the project. But the original source that I literally didn't touch works fine and before my server was working fine too until what happened with Eclipse, all the files are almost identical, I didn't change the code, but for some reason when I build with Eclipse my server gets a bunch of unresolved errors and the original source gets none.
